Sab joining() se possible hai.

Problem

Maan lo List hai

List<String> names = List.of(
        "Rahul",
        "Amit",
        "Neha",
        "Riya"
);

Output chahiye

Rahul, Amit, Neha, Riya

Purane Java me

String result = "";

for(String name : names){

    result += name + ", ";

}

Problems ❌

Slow
Extra comma
Ugly code
String immutable hai

Java 8 ne bola

"Main kar deta hu."

Solution
String result = names.stream()

.collect(Collectors.joining());

System.out.println(result);

Output

RahulAmitNehaRiya

